data.description: Modern luxury meets elegant design in this stunning quick move-in townhome. The open-concept kitchen and great room provide the ideal space for entertaining. The large primary bedroom suite includes a large bath and impressive closet space. Expand your living space with the second-floor loft that is perfectly designed to fit your lifestyle. The lanai and backyard provide ample space, creating the perfect spot for activities, grilling, and outdoor entertaining. Gorgeous designer finishes highlight every room in this home. Disclaimer: Photos are images only and should not be relied upon to confirm applicable features.
